import React from 'react'; import "../styles/styles.scss"; const CurrentWeather = ({temperature, description, city, feels_like, humidity, highTemp, lowTemp}) => {

{Math.round(temperature)}°C

{description}

{city}

Feels like: {Math.round(feels_like)}°C | Humidity: {humidity}
{Math.round(lowTemp)}° / {Math.round(highTemp)}°C
} export default CurrentWeather;
